{"tid":885680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人唔識洗錢真係好辛苦","createTime":"2018-11-01T13:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T14:33:01.000Z","uid":53209,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"deeccaf35309083c6404bc3935b60855c3ea5187","tid":885680,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"朋友有個同事<br />\n20頭/中 月入約3萬<br />\n收入算唔錯 但非常慳<br />\n<br />\n1) 手機用緊note2  mon爆曬 成日聽唔到電話 whatsapp delay<br />\n<br />\n2) 工作上既野 可以用10蚊左右解決 但係都要花半個鐘diy<br />\n<br />\n3) 都係工作上既野  一樣野10蚊以內但可以用好耐 都會因為1-2蚊而周圍問人邊到買平d<br />\n<br />\n4) 食飯a餐40 b餐42 想食b 但會因為貴2蚊而食a<br />\n<br />\n聽個fd講 佢同事小康之家 屋企唔要求比家用咁樣<br />\n<br />\n諗唔明點解一個人要咁苛待自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fb82401392bf204e2f761f653cb1ad447dc1ca","tid":885680,"uid":137096,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"唔通學連登仔咁期期換部皮幾嘢嘅iphone覺得自己先有頭有面先識洗錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd7ab714d2cbe491960ed244314e209bf2891e2","tid":885680,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"人地唔咁慳法點買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bb5ed5d3135238d14bf9c4ff9ee6c1710859a7","tid":885680,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33fb82401392bf204e2f761f653cb1ad447dc1ca","tid":885680,"uid":137096,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"唔通學連登仔咁期期換部皮幾嘢嘅iphone覺得自己先有頭有面先識洗錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"萬幾蚊 我理解 <br />\n我自己都無用緊iPhone 因為我用唔著咁多功能<br />\n但我上面係講緊幾蚊既事<br />\n<br />\n而且個條友唔係揾萬幾要比8000家用個種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10蚊可以解決既野 你曬半個鐘